{"word":"προτιόσσομαι","slug":"προτιόσσομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n90533\" key=\"protio/ssomai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">προτιόσσομαι</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Verb, only <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns>, and never in the form <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">προσόσσομαι</foreign>:—<sense id=\"n90533.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">look at</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">upon</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μηδέ τιν᾽ ἀνθρώπων προτιόσσεο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:7:31\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.31</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:23:365\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.365</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n90533.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of the mind, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">forebode</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κραδίη προτιόσσετ᾽ ὄλεθρον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:389\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.389</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θάνατον προτιόσσετο θυμὸς ἀγήνωρ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:219\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.219</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:895\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.895</biblScope></bibl>, al.; so, prob., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἦ σ᾽ εὖ γιγνώσκων προτιόσσομαι</foreign> from thorough knowledge of thee <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">I divine</tr_> my fate, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:356\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.356</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:1372\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.1372</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}